Syntax: loot <corpse>

Attempts to steal one random item from a player corpse.

Notes:
- You must be level 20+ to use this command.
- You can only loot player corpses (not NPC corpses or other objects).
- The corpse must be lootable for your clan/PK status.
- Loot can fail, and items flagged NOLOOT cannot be taken.
